Photo by Business | Entrepreneurship on September 19, 2021. May be an image of text that says '2. You went through hard times Going through hardships is good! It means you are growing stronger, even if it's tough.'.

Photo by Business | Entrepreneurship on September 19, 2021. May be an image of ‎text that says '‎3. You are serious about your goals Most people don't even know their goals or they just follow the masses. ۔g goals and being serious about them means you are doing way better than you think.‎'‎.

Photo by Business | Entrepreneurship on September 19, 2021. May be an image of text that says '4. You have 1-2 close friends ” friends to count on is a sign that you are blessed- even if it's just one person.'.

Photo by Business | Entrepreneurship on September 19, 2021. May be an image of text that says '5. You seek peace over pleasure Most people just look for that next dopamine hit. If you are seeking peace instead, it means you are far ahead.'.

Photo by Business | Entrepreneurship on September 19, 2021. May be an image of text that says '6. You learn from mistakes Most people run away from their problems or blame others. But you own your mistakes and learn from them.'.

Photo by Business | Entrepreneurship on September 19, 2021. May be an image of text that says '7. You trust that everything will be alright You trust that the universe has great things in store for you and you take action to bring them into reality.'.

Photo by Business | Entrepreneurship on September 18, 2021. May be an image of text that says '3. Whenever something annoys or frustrates you, write down why and what product/service you could make that that would solve it. INVESTEARNSAVE'.

Photo by Business | Entrepreneurship on September 18, 2021. May be an image of text that says '5. Always have something exciting to save money for, to stop you wasting money to gain temporary pleasures. INVESTEARNSAVE'.

Photo by Business | Entrepreneurship on September 18, 2021. May be an image of text that says '6. Find a friend to be your accountability partner- make sure your friend is being productive, saving and investing. INVESTEARNSAVE'.

Photo by Business | Entrepreneurship on September 16, 2021. May be an image of text that says '1. Change how you think about things It all starts in your mind. You can change how you react to what happen in your life.'.

Photo by Business | Entrepreneurship on September 16, 2021. May be an image of text that says '2. Time is finite Remember that you don't have forever and use the precious time you have. Stop staying in a job you hate or being with people you don't care about.'.

Photo by Business | Entrepreneurship on September 16, 2021. May be an image of text that says '3. Develop an attitude of gratitude If you are grateful daily, you'll notice more and more things you can be grateful for. Make gratitude your default state of mind.'.

Photo by Business | Entrepreneurship on September 16, 2021. May be an image of text that says '4. Applied knowledge is power Knowledge alone doesn't give you power. You need to act on it and use what you learned.'.

Photo by Business | Entrepreneurship on September 16, 2021. May be an image of text that says '5. Happiness doesn't come from the material Buying more things won't make you happier long-term. Real happiness is peace.'.

Photo by Business | Entrepreneurship on September 16, 2021. May be an image of text that says '6. Always remember your why If you lost your way or you're struggling right now, start finding your why. It will guide you through the the toughest times.'.

Photo by Business | Entrepreneurship on September 16, 2021. May be an image of text that says '7. Failure is a false belief Failure is just feedback. You did something wrong but now you know better and you can try again.'.

Photo by Business | Entrepreneurship on September 15, 2021. May be an image of text that says '1. Gain Clarity Regularly Clarity helps finding your purpose and vision and exposes any obstacles in your way Το find clarity, take 10 minutes a day to write down your goals and learnings of the day Unplug from social media for at least 1h before you do this to Calm your mind first!'.

Photo by Business | Entrepreneurship on September 15, 2021. May be an image of text that says '2. Practice Gratitude Gratitude is the natural enemy of anxiety, fear, and depression and makes your life brighter: Το practice it, write down five things everyday that you are grateful for. It might be hard at first but you'll get used to it and feel amazing! Stop comparing yourself to others to make sure you don't lose this!'.

Photo by Business | Entrepreneurship on September 15, 2021. May be an image of text that says '3. Stay accountable 97% of the world don't achieve ther goals because they just fall off the bandwagon. Accountability protects you from that. Get a partner to hold you accountable for your goals, and agree on a punishment if you fail or a reward if you Succeed! Don't allow even one slip up or you're back to square one again!'.

Photo by Business | Entrepreneurship on September 15, 2021. May be an image of text that says '4. Practice faith Anything in life that's currently seen as "a fact" can change in an instant. "Humans can't fly," "the sun goes around the earth,' "cars will never replace horses". Those were facts until they weren't Faith helps you achieve your goal even if the current "facts" say you can't do it'.

Photo by Business | Entrepreneurship on September 15, 2021. May be an image of text that says '5. Invest time to grow daily Daily growth makes you feel accomplished, worthy, and better than yesterday. It's very rewarding. Read 10 pages of a self- development book a day Take a course every now and then Watch ted talks and visit seminars If you feel down and worthless you probably didn't grow enough yet today'.

Photo by Business | Entrepreneurship on September 15, 2021. May be an image of text that says '6. See both your strengths and weaknesses It's easy to focus on your shortcomings and forget what you excel at... But your weaknesses help you develop new skills and guide you to people who complete you See weaknesses as growth opportunities!'.

Photo by Business | Entrepreneurship on September 15, 2021. May be an image of text that says '7. Create something impactful Low confidence often comes from feeling like you or your life don't matter If you create something many people enjoy you'll fee better than ever You could craft things and sell them, create a charity or start a business that makes people's lives better'.
